summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning amending Sections 23.30.010, 23.45.008, 23.45.009, 23.45.010, 23.45.011, 23.45.012, 23.45.014, 23.45.016, 23.45.018 and 23.84.048 of the Seattle Municipal Code to add requirements for the development of multifamily structures in a new Lowrise 4 zone.
